		div#features.col-lg-12
			div.container
				h1 Features
				div#announcements.feature
					h2 Announcements
					p Be updated with the latest announcements from the executive department. 
						| Announcements have its own section to ensure that all important 
						| announcements are easily accessed and read by the users.
				div#logbook.feature
					h2 Logbook
					p Have something in your mind? Logbook lets you put your thoughts 
						| into words. Similar to Facebook's status posting feature, 
						| logbook allows you to post which can be viewed by other users.
				div#chat.feature
					h2 Chat
					p Real time chatting is here. Send and receive 
						| chat messages instantly and reliably.
				div#YSERsList.feature
					h2 YSERs List
					p Never forget your orgmates again. YSERs list show all members of 
						| the organization, from Charter members to present! Filter by batch, 
						| filter by org classification, use this tool to fit your recording needs.
				div#department.feature
					h2 Department Systems
					p The main heart and soul of YSES Central. Department systems are 
						| specialized and tailored to each department needs.
					div#department-systems.encloseall.container-fluid.hidden-xs.hidden-sm.hidden-md
						div.gallery
							div#myCarousel.carousel.slide(data-ride="carousel")
								div.carousel-inner
									div.active.item
										h2 EXEC
										h4 Account validator
										p Members must only be YSERs. The Executive Department Members 
											| can review pending signed up accounts and can modify details 
											| for errors. Accept it or reject it!
									div.item
										h2 PAD
										h4 JPAD Progress record
										p Track JPADsters' attendance and score records. 
											| Easily identify those with alarming absences. Recognize outstanding JPADsters.
									div.item
										h2 SEC
										h4 Events Attendance
										p Record attendance of YSERs on required events.
									div.item
										h2 SCHO
										h4 Checklist System
										p No more hand computing GWA of members. 
											| This system allows Scho members to encode YSERs subject and 
											| grades, and the system takes care of the hassle computations 
											| such as members' GWA, overall org GWA, and GWA trends!
									div.item
										h2 VL
										h4 VL Inventory System
										p View and borrow materials from VL
									div.item
										h2 FIN
										h4 Finance System
										p Our beloved Fin System, also in YSES Central. 
											| With more features, such as automatic weekly fees, 
											| dynamic fee allocation, and the ability for users to 
											| view their own current, unpaid fees and previous paid fees.
									div.item
										h2 HR
										h4 Family Tree
										p The whole family tree, displayed in one page. 
											| Know your great-great-great grandfather!
